  function updateCheckboxVal(attrName) {
    if (attrName) {
      var checkboxName = attrName + "_checkbox";
      var intAttr = document.getElementsByName(attrName);
      var intCheckbox = document.getElementsByName(checkboxName);
      if (intCheckbox && intAttr) {
        intAttr[0].value = intCheckbox[0].checked;
      }
    }
  }

  function updatesUponSubmit() {
    var checkboxesInterest = document.querySelectorAll('[data-group="check-box-group-interest"]');
    var guardInterest = false;
    for (var i = 0, l = checkboxesInterest.length; i < l; i++) {
      if (checkboxesInterest[i].checked) {
        guardInterest = true;
        break;
      }
    }

    var checkboxesComms = document.querySelectorAll('[data-group="check-box-group-comms"]');
    var guardComms = false;
    for (var i = 0, l = checkboxesComms.length; i < l; i++) {
      if (checkboxesComms[i].checked) {
        guardComms = true;
        break;
      }
    }

    if (guardInterest && guardComms) {
      var gmt8Date = new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-US", { timeZone: "Asia/Singapore" });
      const now = new Date().toUTCString();
      var optinEmailDate = document.getElementsByName("OptinEmailDate");
      var createdDate = document.getElementsByName("CreatedDate");
      var formSubmissionDate = document.getElementsByName("FormSubmissionDate");
      var primaryKey = document.getElementsByName("PrimaryKey");
      var getEmail = document.getElementById("email").value;
      var getWebsource = document.getElementById("websourceID").value;
      optinEmailDate[0].value = now;
      createdDate[0].value = now;
      formSubmissionDate[0].value = now;
      primaryKey[0].value = getEmail + getWebsource + gmt8Date;

      updateCheckboxVal("Interest_BCD");
      updateCheckboxVal("Interest_ENG");
      updateCheckboxVal("Interest_FCB");
      updateCheckboxVal("Interest_HSS");
      updateCheckboxVal("Interest_ICT");

      updateCheckboxVal("Comms_SITLEARN");
      updateCheckboxVal("Comms_Undergraduate");
      updateCheckboxVal("Comms_Postgraduate");

      //Unlink the unfilled checkbox to DEManager to prevent overwrite
      if (document.getElementById("Interest_BCD_ID").value == "false") {
        document.getElementById("Interest_BCD_ID").value = "";
      }
      if (document.getElementById("Interest_ENG_ID").value == "false") {
        document.getElementById("Interest_ENG_ID").value = "";
      }
      if (document.getElementById("Interest_FCB_ID").value == "false") {
        document.getElementById("Interest_FCB_ID").value = "";
      }
      if (document.getElementById("Interest_HSS_ID").value == "false") {
        document.getElementById("Interest_HSS_ID").value = "";
      }
      if (document.getElementById("Interest_ICT_ID").value == "false") {
        document.getElementById("Interest_ICT_ID").value = "";
      }
      if (document.getElementById("Comms_SITLEARN_ID").value == "false") {
        document.getElementById("Comms_SITLEARN_ID").value = "";
      }
      if (document.getElementById("Comms_Undergraduate_ID").value == "false") {
        document.getElementById("Comms_Undergraduate_ID").value = "";
      }
      if (document.getElementById("Comms_Postgraduate_ID").value == "false") {
        document.getElementById("Comms_Postgraduate_ID").value = "";
      }
    } else {
      var checkboxes = document.querySelector('.error-message');
      checkboxes.classList.add('active');
      return false;
    }

  }
